Pre-Sale Success: Launched on April 8, 2024, at the Hong Kong Web3 Carnival, the first round of pre-sales sold 12,000 Founding Series phones in three days. Pre-orders were priced at $99, with a referral program offering up to $12 per invite and $OYS rewards.

Refunds and Transparency: Oyster Labs processed full refunds for 6,000 randomly selected UBS buyers while retaining their benefits (phone delivery and Passes). The company emphasizes transparency with daily reports and direct NGO hotlines for content moderation.

Free Upgrades: All previous UBS buyers are eligible for a free upgrade to the UBS1, featuring improved hardware and design.

